            Connect anonymously with trusted psychologists when you need it most.
        </p>
        
        <div class="animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
            <a href="/onboarding" class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg shadow-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
                Start Your Journey
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
